Category:Unidentified Sith of the One Sith

nodes.text: A member of Darth Krayt's One Sith, this Rodian Sith was one of four Sith who ambushed four Jedi (Rasi Tuum, Wolf Sazen, Shado Vao, and one other) on the planet Daluuj in 137 ABY. He was decapitated by Shado Vao at the end of the skirmish.
